## Strategic Content Analysis: **Decoding Netflix’s Global Streaming Logic**
This project is an end-to-end technical deep dive into Netflix’s content ecosystem, designed to move beyond simple data retrieval and uncover the business drivers behind a global streaming giant. By transforming raw datasets into structured intelligence, I engineered a suite of Advanced SQL solutions to track content lifecycles, production shifts, and audience engagement patterns.

## The Technical Framework
- **Data Engineering & Optimization:** Architected the dataset to handle multi-dimensional content attributes, ensuring the schema was optimized for high-performance analytical queries and scalable reporting.
- **Advanced Analytical Problem-Solving:** Systematically addressed mission-critical business questions—from automated content categorization to Year-over-Year (YoY) growth metrics—using sophisticated SQL workflows.
- **Algorithmic Insights:** Leveraged Window Functions, Common Table Expressions (CTEs), and Regex/String Manipulation to identify non-obvious patterns in genre saturation and directorial consistency.

